	<td bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	<td class="subjectbar" height="20" style="font-size: 8pt;padding-left:10px;" width="100%">
		Proposed Revamp to help bring Aego type buffs into line more realistically...

	</td>
	
		<td class="subjectbar" align=right style="padding:0px;padding-right:10px;">












		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0 id="io_bclericbalancem8457_table" 
		
			onClick="setId('8457');showLiMenu(this,'io_bclericbalancem8457','right',false);" 
			onDblClick="setId('8457');showLiMenu(this,'io_bclericbalancem8457','right',false);" 
			
		>
		<tr class=clickable>
			
				<td nowrap><a class=subjectbar_text style='font-size: 8pt;'>Options</a></td>
				
			<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
			<td><img src='/i/skins/default/button_options.gif' border=0 alt='Options' title='Options' width=11 height=28></td>
			<td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		</td></tr>
		
	<tr>
	
		<td class="msg_user_cell" width="150" valign=top>
		
			 









<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=32770'  class="auth_text"  style="font-weight:bold;" >	
<span style='color:#336600;'>Mediik7th</span></a>
			<br>
			
			<span style="font-size: 8pt;">
			Journeyman<br>
			
				Posts: 82<br>
				
				Registered: 05-10-2004
				
			</span>
			


			
			<br>
			
				<img src="/i/p.gif" height=8 width=150 border=0 alt=""><br>
				
			<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=32770'>







</a><br>
			


			
			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=clericbalance&message.id=8457#M8457">1</a> of 18
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 503 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>I hate to see a spell like Aegolism fall by the wayside.&nbsp; It was&nbsp;THE cleric&nbsp;buff for so long, there is surely a useful place for it in the cleric lineup with a little help. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The problem as it looks to me, there are just simply too many buffs all crammed together in the 50's.&nbsp;Spells which aren't getting used,&nbsp;because now with POK, corpse summoning, gate potions, TL's&nbsp;etc etc....&nbsp;access to buffs isn't limited to your immediate group or area as it once was when travel around Norrath was such a hardship.&nbsp; Most people stop by POK and get the buff's they need beforehand, making alot of in between spells less than useful.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>As a result&nbsp;as your leveling up.&nbsp;The buffs are useable, meaning.. how long the cleric can cast these spells on himself, before it becomes more beneficial to get a higher level cleric buff.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Spell&nbsp;&nbsp;: First level useable&nbsp;: Number of useable levels</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Temp&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Cleric gets at 40 (5 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>Aego&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 45&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp; Cleric gets at 60 (0 Useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>Virt&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 46&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp; Cleric gets at 62 (0 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>Conv&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;62&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp; &nbsp;Cleric gets at 67 (4 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>So if I'm reading this right, based on these main spells,&nbsp;a cleric only benefits from buffing himself 9 out of 70 levels..&nbsp;the other&nbsp;61 levels, he's in POK looking for the higher level cleric buff as are other&nbsp;classes his or her level.&nbsp; If I've lost you.. your not alone hehe... keep reading.&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Anyway.. I propose the following:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Lower Temperance to level&nbsp;29 - </DIV>
<DIV>Lower Group Temp to level&nbsp;32 - </DIV>
<DIV>Lower Aegolism to level&nbsp;49 -&nbsp;&nbsp;decrease the castable&nbsp;level 40 (from 45)</DIV>
<DIV>Lower Group Aego to level&nbsp; 52 -&nbsp;decrease the castable&nbsp;level 40 (from 45)</DIV>
<DIV>Leave Ancient Aego at level 60 - double the duration of the spell and decrease the castable level to 40 (from 45)</DIV>
<DIV>Leave Virtue at 62 -&nbsp;increase the castable level to 55 (from 46)</DIV>
<DIV>Leave Conviction 67 - Leave the castable level at 62</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>This would have the following result on the previous chart:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Temp -&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp;Cleric gets at 29(11 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>Aego&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; 40&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; Cleric gets at 49(6 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>Virtue -&nbsp;&nbsp; 55&nbsp; -&nbsp;&nbsp; Cleric gets at 62(0 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>Conv -&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;62&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;&nbsp; Cleric gets at 67(4 useable levels)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>After making these changes, the cleric&nbsp;can now&nbsp;buff himself 21&nbsp;out of 70&nbsp;instead of previous 9.&nbsp; Also&nbsp;Aego was brought back into the mix again.</DIV>
<DIV>Now you may ask.. what about the intermediate spells?&nbsp; What about em?&nbsp; When was the last time you were asked for a Courage?? Or Heroism??&nbsp;Just cut some of the fat and dump em.&nbsp; Well maybe not all of them, but I don't think it's necessary to go into that much detail at this time. I would also&nbsp;suggest something similar to the Symbol line, but my head already hurts.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Thanks for reading</DIV>
<DIV>Mediik - The&nbsp;Seventh Hammer&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>	
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
